OL,3,CParkinson's: 'I'm going to fight it
OL,4,Cand have a jolly good time while doing
OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FWhen Dario Bucceri was diagnosed with
OL,8,F's in 2019, he was devastated.
OL,10,FHe believed the neurological disorder
OL,11,Fwould negatively impact every aspect
OL,12,Fof his life.
OL,14,FHowever, upon moving to in north
OL,15,FWales, Dario decided to embrace life
OL,16,Fwith Parkinson's and find different
OL,17,Fmethods to help him accept this new
OL,18,Freality.
