OL,3,CParkinson's: 'I'm going to fight it
OL,4,Cand have a jolly good time while doing
OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FSpeaking to ITV Wales, he said: "We
OL,8,Ffound the canal close to the house. So
OL,9,Fshortly after we moved here, I bought
OL,10,Fmyself a kayak and I come up here to
OL,11,Fexercise and to spend time with my
OL,12,Fson."
OL,14,F"I think it helps with my movement.
OL,15,FParkinson's takes big things and makes
OL,16,Fthem small. So it's good for me to
OL,17,Fpaddle and go through those motions,
OL,18,Fand just to be in a quiet environment
OL,19,Flike this."
OL,21,FDario's own journey has not been easy.
