OL,3,CParkinson's: 'I'm going to fight it
OL,4,Cand have a jolly good time while doing
OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,FHe said his wife initially noticed his
OL,8,Fright arm was not swinging when he
OL,9,Fwalked. This, coupled with a
OL,10,Fdeteriorating sense of smell and
OL,11,Ftaste, as well as a loss of dexterity
OL,12,Fin his hands, led him to seek medical
OL,13,Fadvice.
OL,15,FHe said: "I got to the point where I
OL,16,Fwas down and depressed about it. But,
OL,17,Fone day, I decided that this had to be
OL,18,Fdifferent and that I'd make it the
OL,19,Fbest thing that's ever happened to me.
