OL,3,CParkinson's: 'I'm going to fight it
OL,4,Cand have a jolly good time while doing
OL,5,Cit'
OL,7,F"It's a choice. I'm either going to
OL,8,Flet this thing take me out, or I'm
OL,9,Fgoing to fight it every inch of the
OL,10,Fway and have a jolly good time while
OL,11,Fdoing it!"
OL,13,FCommitted to maintaining his active
OL,14,Flifestyle, as well as kayaking, Dario
OL,15,Fhopes to climb Snowdon. He has also
OL,16,Fran a number of marathons to raise
OL,17,Ffunds for charities.
OL,19,FParkinson's is the fastest growing
OL,20,Fneurological condition in the world,
OL,21,Fand currently there is no cure.
