OL,7,F1 in 37 people alive today in the UK
OL,8,Fwill be diagnosed with the condition
OL,9,Fin their lifetime.
OL,11,FAna Palazon, Parkinson's UK Director
OL,12,Ffor Wales told ITV Wales: "For some
OL,13,Fpeople, having the diagnosis can be
OL,14,Fquite shocking and devastating. It is
OL,15,Fa life changing diagnosis, and for
OL,16,Fsome people, it can take a while to
OL,17,Fdigest and gradually get used to a new
OL,18,Freality."
